                    <note type="abstract" xml:id="abstract-en-50">
                        <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/50">John of Tella</persName> was a monk and <seg source="#bib50-1">Bishop of Tella (d-Mawzlat) (519-521)</seg> 
                        who had to flee his see on account of the aggression of the Chalcedonians. 
                        With <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/69">Jacob Baradaeus</persName>, <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/50">John of Tella</persName> ordained a new clergy of Miaphysite clergy.
